<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbce4b83a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s4854b"><num value="4854b">§ 4854b.</num><heading> Authorization</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Of the total amount approved in appropriation Acts under section 4852(<i>o</i>) <ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn003377">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn003377"><num>1</num> See References in Text note below.</note> of this title, there shall be set aside to carry out this part $5,000,000 for fiscal year 1993, and $5,000,000 for fiscal year 1994.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbce4b83b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/550/tX/s1053">Pub. L. 102–550, title X, § 1053</ref>, <date date="1992-10-28">Oct. 28, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/3926">106 Stat. 3926</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbce4b83c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
