<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="idbce4b83e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section 4852(<i>o</i>) of this title, referred to in text, was redesignated <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s4852/p">section 4852(p) of this title</ref> by <ref href="/us/pl/103/233/tIII/s305/a/1">Pub. L. 103–233, title III, § 305(a)(1)</ref>, <date date="1994-04-11">Apr. 11, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/370">108 Stat. 370</ref>.</p>
